    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been meticulously calibrated for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure torsional rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, with bushings and dampers providing the communicative feedback expected of a low-mileage, collector-grade vehicle. The exterior retains its original luster with uniform paint depth, while the interior leather shows no signs of compression or bolster wear. Zero deferred maintenance and a pristine underbody make this a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
